              <div class="desc"> Hello! My name is Matthew Haslem. I am an aspiring Web Developer with over a decade worth of experience in both front-end and back-end development. I am currently a student studying Computer Science at Old Dominion University. I expect to graduate in December of 2021 and use this degree, along with my first (B.S. in Communications), to secure a career somewhere in the Computer Science field. </div>
